  <description>{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\deff0\nouicompat\deflang1033{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset0 Microsoft Sans Serif;}}
{\*\generator Riched20 10.0.19041}\viewkind4\uc1 
\pard\f0\fs17 short?\par
Hair has rosette from skin pigmentation that is visible over her face and shoulders\par
\par
}
