  <background>{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\deff0\nouicompat\deflang1033{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset0 Microsoft Sans Serif;}}
{\*\generator Riched20 10.0.19041}\viewkind4\uc1 
\pard\f0\fs17 Born in france. When the Surge event 14 years ago (2061) Halley\rquote s Comet caused SURGE. Character and other members of her community were affected. (See bellow)\par
Family moved over the border from France to German after the SURGE event divided the comunity they were living in.\par
Joined a new SURGE community in Germany.\par
Taught to shoot (firearms 6) and hunt by father and community. Learned how to farm. Recived an education online. Good with Technology/Computers.\par
As an Adult she left the community to enter the world. Shunned as a SINless and a changeling she fell back on skills learned as a hunter.\par
Intro to Shadowrunning. The Burlin Sprawl became her concrete jungle.\par
Started off with a cheap rifle and commlink.\par
Earned the Nuyen to but mods and upgraded her weapon herself.\par
Worked on Sniper hots, survalience and theft.\par
Found use in a shit hits the fan close quarters weapon in a smg.\par
Ran solo, so ran into issue without Matrix support.\par
Took a loan to buy a deck.\par
On a run H\'f6llen had the Oppertunity to steal some nice cyberware, and took it.\par
Muscule Replacement Rating 2 and Wired Reflexes Rating 1 were stolen.\par
By the time she had gotten home with the loot, a bounty had been placed on her head (Stolen Gear 10 - \'a5 50 000) and in the next few days the first attack happened.\par
H\'f6llen decided it was to hot to stay and moved. After finding a place to hide she had the cyberware installed.\par
Running away from bounty hunters has led to H\'f6llen leaving Germany and ending up in the Netherlands.\par
\par
Possible intro could be the people she borrowed money from hiring her on to work in the Netherlands.\par
\par
}
</background>
  <concept>{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\deff0\nouicompat\deflang1033{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset0 Microsoft Sans Serif;}}
{\*\generator Riched20 10.0.19041}\viewkind4\uc1 
\pard\f0\fs17 Loner due to her outsider status. She is used to performing solo misions. Sniper, snoop, spy and thief. Picked up some decking to protect her cyberware and equipment.\par
}
</concept>
  <notes>{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\deff0\nouicompat\deflang1033{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset0 Microsoft Sans Serif;}}
{\*\generator Riched20 10.0.19041}\viewkind4\uc1 
\pard\f0\fs17 Cat Person (Changeling Metatype) General Qualities\par
\par
Positive Metagenic Qualities (28)\par
Balance Receptor 6\par
Broadened Auditory System (Ultrasound) 4\par
Functional Tail (Balance) 6\par
Keen-Eared 3\par
Low-Light Vision (Feline) 2\par
Retractable Claws 7\par
\par
Negative Metagenic Qualities (22)\par
Berserker 6\par
Critter Spook 5\par
Nocturnal 4\par
Striking Skin Pigmentation 4 (stripes/spots/rosette)\par
Unusual Hair 3 (colour/more hair cover/manes/full body fur)\par
}
</notes>
